com.simiacryptus.mindseye.eval

Class BasicTrainable

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.eval.BasicTrainable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataTrainable, Trainable, TrainableDataMask

    public class BasicTrainable
extends Object
implements DataTrainable, TrainableDataMask
    This class handles dispatching network evaluations, and distributing the evaluations to the system GPU(s). This is the main class the handles actual execution for training purposes.

      • gcEachIteration

        protected boolean gcEachIteration
        Between each iteration we have the option to initiate a garbage collection. This is a good opportunity since the reachable object count will be at a minimum between collections, making GC more efficient. This can be configured as a non-blocking operation by using the JVM flags "-XX:+ExplicitGCInvokesConcurrent -XX:+UseConcMarkSweepGC"
